summary: WHILE DRIVING ON A HIGHWAY WITH A SPEED LIMIT OF 65 MPH AND HEAVY TRAFFIC, ALL OF THE SUDDEN MY VEHICLE WOULD NOT SHIFT OUT OF 3RD GEAR. ONCE I REACHED AROUND 40MPH AND TRIED TO ACCELERATE I FELT KNOCK AND SHAKING. THE ENGINE WOULD CONTINUE TO REV, HOWEVER NO ACCELERATION OR SHIFTING WOULD HAPPEN. IT BEGINS TO SPUTTER AND FEELS AS THOUGHT THE VEHICLE IS GOING TO SHUT OFF.
